{"root":{"data":{"id":"dh0oixst3t40","created":1773306034199,"text":"测试数据的几大原因"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0oncjdnq80","created":1773306379737,"text":"研究生阶段的能力铺垫","layout_mind_offset":{"x":29.16666434870845,"y":15.999998964369212},"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0p1qo7wps0","created":1773307507603,"text":"mems的使用练习，后续实验使用mems能够迅速上手","layout_right_offset":{"x":60.25000156338035,"y":-63.58333401092227}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0tr7sycbc0","created":1773320788439,"text":"分支主题","layout_right_offset":{"x":91.00000180800782,"y":0}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dh0onejsx5k0","created":1773306384116,"text":"加强毕设本身的理解","layout_mind_offset":{"x":33.249999449898894,"y":110.5000019346677}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0ongf51wo0","created":1773306388188,"text":"实际技术需求","layout_mind_offset":{"x":1190.2500154984518,"y":-248.50000340988305},"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0ozlkz49k0","created":1773307339794,"text":"多轴运动\n楼梯+斜坡实验\n上下楼梯（3-5层）和上下斜坡（坡度5°-15°）\n高度误差、水平投影误差、垂直方向零速检测率","layout_right_offset":{"x":141.8333330137864,"y":74.33333183411128}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0vg6pebs00","created":1773325566260,"text":"航向误差\n长距离/多转弯实验\n设计包含多个直角弯的闭合路径（如矩形走5圈），观察每圈结束时的航向偏差累积\n每圈航向角误差、终点闭合误差","layout_right_offset":{"x":152.9999986688303,"y":-208.6666626003062}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0veukyr740","created":1773325461507,"text":"多步速对比实验\n对比验证这几种零速检测方法在不同步速下的检测能力","layout_right_offset":{"x":118.99999922265744,"y":-566.1666288963637}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0vf76wwrk0","created":1773325488955,"text":"脚底缓冲实验","layout_right_offset":{"x":165.3333324376085,"y":-544.6666599454165}},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}